txt.en: Melethon is at the Causeway Forts.\n\nYou should speak to Melethon.

'The time has come to retake the Eastern Wharf! I need every soldier to stand with me as we march upon the enemy.\n\n'Go and defeat as many foes as you can at the Eastern Wharf. We shall take back this city!'
Defeat minions of Mordor at the Eastern Wharf ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Melethon has ordered you to fight and slaughter foes around the Eastern Wharf in the goal to retake Osgiliath.
'You have done much for the Gondorian army. Victory will surely be ours!'
The Eastern Wharf is located on the Eastern side of Osgiliath.\n\nYou should fight and slaughter foes around the Eastern Wharf.
